childDownloads.title: Kameo Demo
childDownloads.description: Pummel, charge and spear your way through the Kameo Demo! Experience the epic adventure from legendary developer Rare, Ltd.

childDownloads.title: Kameo Design-A-Skin Pack
childDownloads.description: You’ve seen what Rare can do; now find out what the designers of tomorrow came up with for the Kameo Design-A-Skin Contest!  Enjoy 11 all-new skins for Kameo and her Warriors based on designs from the games’ fans!  Download this free pack now and find out what Ash would look like as a Griffin, what happens when you mix Snare with a giant cobra, and why poor Thermite feels as though he has the weight of the world on his shoulders!

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ 40 Below Video
childDownloads.description: See what moves Kameo's coldest elemental warrior has hidden up his icy sleeves. Watch 40 Below own the battlefield, freezing trolls with Frost Bite and dishing massive destruction with Snow Blower and Wrecker Ball. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Chilla Video
childDownloads.description: See what moves Kameo's feistiest elemental warrior has at his disposal. Watch Chilla bust out his Ice Spike for long-ranged sniping, take down hordes with powerful Spike Storms, and even impale enemies on his back with SpikeBack. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Combos Video
childDownloads.description: See Kameo's various elemental warriors combine their moves to unleash massive destruction on their enemies. Learn to pull off these combos consistently and you'll have truly mastered Kameo's morphing abilities. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Deep Blue Video
childDownloads.description: See Kameo's seasoned elemental warrior make waves with various moves. Watch Deep Blue dive into the fray, blowing away underwater foes with his Aqua Blaster torpedoes and blasting enemies with his Aqua Cannon. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Flex Video
childDownloads.description: See Kameo's most elastic elemental warrior at his tentacled best. Watch Flex grab enemies with Sucka Shot, then hurl them with Flingshot, bash them into the ground with Sucka Slam, or electrocute them with Shocker.  (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Major Ruin Video
childDownloads.description: See Kameo's veteran elemental warrior throw his weight around. Watch Major Ruin impale multiple enemies with Razor Back and hammer through even the toughest opposition with Boulder Rush. Bowling for trolls, anyone? (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Pummel Weed Video
childDownloads.description: See what moves Kameo's greenest elemental warrior can deliver. Watch Pummel Weed knock out opponents with Jab and Uprooter, control armored or explosive shells with Shredder, and slice through enemies with Weed Creeper. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Rubble Video
childDownloads.description: See what moves Kameo's boldest elemental warrior can rock out to. Watch Rubble break out of large mobs with Gravel Blast, plaster enemies with the lethal Stone Storm, and pick off foes with Sling Stone and Stone Chip. (Not Rated)

childDownloads.title: Kameo™: Elements of Power™ Thermite Video
childDownloads.description: See Kameo's smallest elemental warrior dish fiery heat. Watch Thermite move quickly in the invincible Blast Shield mode, rain Lava Bombs with Mortar mode, create pools of fire with Fire Burst, and suck up and launch enemies. (Not Rated)
